txt.en:
This item will complete certain quests available in Gondor, granting the Class Trait Points they come with.

<rgb=#FF7700>Requires you to have used the Aria of the Valar Level-up item.</rgb>

<rgb=#ff0000>If you use this item, this character can never play the following quests and deeds</rgb>

This completes the quests and deeds:

'Ashes and Stars, Chapter 4'
'A Ruthless End'
'Sons of the Usurper'
'Faltharan's Confrontation'
